title: React Best Practices
content:
Important React patterns and best practices to remember:

**Component Structure:**
• Use functional components with hooks
• Keep components small and focused
• Use proper prop types or TypeScript
• Implement proper error boundaries

**State Management:**
• Use useState for local state
• Consider useReducer for complex state
• Context API for global state
• Redux for large applications

**Performance:**
• Use React.memo for expensive renders
• Implement proper key props in lists
• Lazy load components when possible
• Optimize bundle size with code splitting

**Testing:**
• Write unit tests for components
• Integration tests for user flows
• Use React Testing Library

title: Fitness Goals 2024
content:
My fitness goals and workout plan for this year:

**Goals:**
• Lose 15 pounds
• Run a 5K in under 25 minutes
• Increase strength by 20%
• Improve flexibility and mobility

**Weekly Schedule:**
• Monday: Upper body strength training
• Tuesday: 30-minute run
• Wednesday: Yoga or stretching
• Thursday: Lower body strength training
• Friday: Rest or light walk
• Saturday: Long run or hiking
• Sunday: Active recovery

**Nutrition:**
• Drink 8 glasses of water daily
• Eat 5 servings of fruits and vegetables
• Limit processed foods
• Meal prep on Sundays

**Progress Tracking:**
• Weigh in weekly
• Track workouts in app
• Take progress photos monthly
